snippet.title: Smitty's Journey - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The wait... is over. Smitty is finally here and ready to roll! After over 2 years of development (and originally planned to be an anniversary-centric title), Smitty's Journey is finally ready to get yourself entertained.

Join Smitty as he travels through Dripsdale, encountering unusual creatures, discovering secrets of the world and even some odd mechanical marvels.


Available on:
- itch.io: https://sonargames.itch.io/smittys-journey
- Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/smittysjourney/467895
- Kartridge: https://www.kartridge.com/games/tetriser016/smittys-journey


========

Website: https://sonargamesmy.wordpress.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/K95ETXX
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Tetriser_SONAR
